en_840095_0	Old Royalists Union of Piliyandala, responding positively to a request, made by Major General Darshana Hettiarachchi, Commander, Security Forces - Jaffna donated a stock of school accessories to 125 students at Nelliadi Central College on the National Independence Day (4 Feb).
en_840095_1	To coincide with the National Independence Day, 4 Sri Lanka Sinha Regiment (SLSR) troops of the 551 Brigade under the 55 Division took the initiative of organizing the donation programme in close contact with school authorities.
en_840095_2	Colonel Asanka Perera, 551 Brigade Commander as the Chief Guest, together with representatives of the sponsors and Lieutenant Colonel Pinsara Wickramarachchi, Commanding Officer 4 SLSR attended the donation programme.
